{"hd542732dged0cg4f7ega6bcgd5b611566a0f": ["Looking at something?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "4d8a46c9-1d64-fb5e-cf67-226a51824fdc"], "h2bbdef0ag0fe1g488bga792g7f226dbfb4d6": ["How did you know I was here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "feaa65da-6a80-f560-54b2-8b30e3ee7453"], "haf3ee765gc7abg4e72g8033gc1755ab4ac8b": ["The only benefit to a mirror when you have my condition.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "b96ec4d0-ea8d-94b0-6745-0f2f4a6c9520"], "h080c3119gbc86g440bg86f2gf24708f2a662": ["It doesn't quite make up for the lack of a reflection, mind you.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "e028a110-ced8-8ca9-8b5b-fb5ef2181ead"], "h2ec3bf9bgbfc5g4b13g88a4g4e3fcac7da94": ["Do you miss it? Seeing your own face?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "3955c822-53b3-813f-7e57-027205fbaa38"], "hfbad7f99g9c4bg4ce5g8a5fge23bdd34f4f7": ["Preening in the looking glass? Petty vanity? Of course I miss it.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "ffe8f6bb-42a9-010c-449d-30bbc6aa2b6c"], "h6d155891ge8cdg4ccdg8885gd8d32ccab5a2": ["I've never even seen this face. Not since it grew fangs and my eyes turned red.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "5395740b-6d21-c186-b5ea-814e479dc84e"], "h6d59f7ccg7034g4588gb6aagc374639c8ab3": ["What colour were they before?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "cc590e39-e6d4-a000-93e4-16a25a92942b"], "h8b6f00c1g3888g45edg9f88gfa3bf2ac8709": ["I... I don't know. I can't remember.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "dbd47f00-5b42-08ee-c89d-fa87bf46c7ad"], "ha6482c6ag7df2g427fg9c99gddba50397bd5": ["My face is just some dark shape in my past. Another thing I've lost.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "99d88343-321d-0396-e8ee-ba3fe00c1998"], "h2bdaaac2geddbg4e45gbf1bg2db4b5ca51ee": ["<i>Stare into his eyes, taking in every detail of his face.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "44834d41-c724-ef7e-c2f8-87630a66cd01"], "h49b4d54cgaf98g47d3g8e90ga587057d6a59": ["What?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "bb89be87-b6ff-0669-dd24-9eaf39d62613"], "h356cce95gddf6g4799ga4a2gecf736984897": ["I see you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "23b45bed-7901-477a-d8a5-c4bd956c383d"], "h210f9c32g3398g4ae3g81e9ge42c9b2ed5bc": ["And what do you see, exactly?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "f36802e0-9b76-919f-b081-57560dac326e"], "ha38cc47egf0f3g48ffgb347g483fdbf925fe": ["Strong, piercing eyes.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "d95449ed-3ce8-7c20-099d-d85fdd764e4a"], "h10064e3bgb0a6g4593gb68ag6df612812118": ["Oh. Go on...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "795da8b6-c9f6-3dcc-7ba8-f9c18360b795"], "h88c136f2g67bbg4ea5g8cd8g7b1ad3b1907b": ["That dangerous smile.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "9015adf4-6367-ecff-d3bb-ee056151c41f"], "h0e06e63bg478cg4b12ga76fg299363adfba3": ["Very good. Now just tell me I'm beautiful and we can call it a day.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "1d0f0bca-02a8-7817-3149-fa43fe46d237"], "h0f8c7372g5364g4254g90abgacc17a17ea6e": ["You're beautiful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "5fc6e329-2246-8090-ba76-08ab6aa46165"], "ha6664d2cgdbc3g4c56gbcf7gdf5647959107": ["Observant.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "69b92f3a-2296-522f-eeba-a6de718e02fc"], "h8c830e01gc0feg4137gb2c4g7a0ef0f854b2": ["Mirrors aren't much use, but being reflected in someone else's eyes?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "3f744589-2842-8783-782f-811c192ce61e"], "hd74b0740gb216g46eagacd5g242c163b39cf": ["Well, I could do worse.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "f5faa5a2-bc10-425a-8399-ad26bdea5a3b"], "ha27c74a4g0821g4d39g958eg36d2bad5930e": ["You're pretty good. Not 'Gale' good, but pretty good.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "0f8a26c8-95f0-340f-6d4c-bd57e14a176b"], "h5874b2fcgbc9fg4bfdg8380gf668a51834e8": ["How dare you! I thought we had something special.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "5e7ee629-f316-19c0-71a5-cefd51f8fc8c"], "he21ce101gc43eg4e95gb9ffgef0b25907335": ["Still. You're nice too.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "f2c7efec-8a3c-ca0a-b4ff-650b2aabb2cb"], "h9ce300b6g6f23g4f08g87abg9ab1c95fa8d6": ["I'd better get some beauty sleep. It seems I need it if I'm to catch up with the competition.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "3d791fcc-b6b4-9dc0-5df0-11cd77086901"], "h2bbbaa44ga28bg4430g8f3ag31bb6e847ee4": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "600af61f-a0aa-9789-4136-40ca2bfb25d1"], "h8b1e3433g3e87g45d3gb255g4e116b0689bf": ["Karlach is beautiful. You're fine, though.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "8d91c3b7-810e-6825-ea7a-c5365560d58f"], "hbc582720g1155g4ec6g95a0gc2e427d626dc": ["You don't have Lae'zel's charm, but you're all right.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "a578116e-efca-16b3-680b-f01eb895fac6"], "ha6ebca13g7c50g4d23gad87g3075865713ca": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "52b55c5f-e49b-8e06-3dd9-6c100009498d"], "hd2011626geeaag4da0g8875g113dcbb656de": ["You're fine. Now Shadowheart - there's a beauty!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "d29f8343-79f9-0bad-74d1-2cc03b1b5737"], "h907960ddg550fg442fgaf91gdd8ed2db18c3": ["Honestly, Wyll's more my type.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "9d1801af-3108-a67c-8a42-5ee8db2c44f9"], "h21b4da8bg8b0dg46fag90dag3263edbad2c3": ["Is that all you want? Shallow praise?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "7b94a9da-a259-fba2-bf22-9b9ce085cff4"], "h9b103618ge8a7g4aaeg9aacgb676fbd0d0b5": ["Hardly. There's also gold, sex, revenge - quite the list, really.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "c0ff68b0-6401-acb3-5a04-0610996893b4"], "h823b3ecdgc0cdg4f38gb87dge48a9a3b0a4e": ["But failing any of those, I will always settle for shallow praise.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "87ff83af-8787-9c26-61bf-6c17fcc35f26"], "h0c2ff412g7823g4f42gaf51g8dece61cb7f6": ["The way your hair curls around your ears.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "cb0842e3-1814-1270-0979-8694a7c1a4ca"], "h8cf3c77bgf30bg46fagba92g02293240d2c1": ["This is meant to be flattery, not poetry. Just tell me I'm beautiful and we can call it a day.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "01e97b37-bd06-beb6-9fd7-4815f1fc3f70"], "h5a83732bge987g4d78g9fb1gd4f0d53494e8": ["Your unsightly mole...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "57148c04-e887-0bb4-dfe8-f08a0412035f"], "hd4e4f35ag7f61g42e5gaf50gdf5be6a21bb3": ["My - what? But I don't...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "c1521905-0327-7bf8-49a9-5d0a17269c6e"], "h83f7857egde7cg439egb910g66e824bb9e66": ["... Excuse me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "bf70c6ea-88e7-bc77-4ce9-94a7d736bc96"], "h60594070g73ddg4c99g98fag7b76b894ea42": ["The creases when you laugh.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "7446aec6-c1c0-d462-c7a9-601846ac6ec3"], "hbb6922c1g0943g46e9g8e57gfe097b4e9ce0": ["Excuse me? I'm an eternally young vampire, not your doting grandmother.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "9d14c79a-02e5-d47d-52eb-fd38bd64bddc"], "hd888ba3fg71e7g45c6g8dfdg0f0f70b6a1e4": ["You can do better. What else?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "85aa2854-e4b0-2589-00f8-187e49ecade3"], "hcde3f7d5g96e6g4802g8127g108b73943b76": ["Your mole definitely grabs my attention.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "20a8cb3d-eb3b-c030-20db-8f819cd5b7fc"], "ha4cc3088ga37fg4fe7gba22gb7503a15a10b": ["An elven vampire spawn, approximately 5'11\", medium build...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "38d413c0-f1bc-fcb2-91d1-66551fe8b6ae"], "hc88a63eeg083ag40b5g96cbg3895cf14e605": ["Gods above. Would it kill you to dispense a compliment?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "dde71352-41a3-d643-405b-94b087763c12"], "hc777e7beg3f56g42e5g967cg9517005a3093": ["Your eyes are pleasing.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "dcba9124-47e3-efb2-1bbf-e59d1d550e1e"], "hec90c374g6f93g4087g856dg89f3819cafb6": ["When you smile, your face wrinkles. It is comforting.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "3e9cfad5-a50e-b031-2d82-bd1e6f9d0d3a"], "he3a086d9gbc19g4f45g8eabg7a662c0b9f92": ["Despite being neither brave nor intelligent, you are one of the finest killers I've ever seen.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "af3f9c01-7389-4ba7-37fc-336910740a78"], "h43eb97bcg943dg4d49gaa91g9fd17371c1f8": ["... Right. I, um...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "e37f1f28-abf7-6faa-4293-3e823cac1d53"], "hbe904425gf4ddg4beegafdfgecd32c7c51f4": ["Let's leave it there, shall we? It's been a long day and I've had all the compliments I can take.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "c3a4fffd-1fd8-89d3-189a-7c50bf8f462a"], "h485cd98fgd4dcg4ac2gbb87gf32e4c6f7e19": ["Your mole is impressively large.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "3ed8090d-5bae-071f-56f3-e2609db82c9a"], "h5ecfdb7cg29c6g4ef3g8a7cg15e815d28d99": ["I see someone wasting my time.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "6be6a98c-8187-c63d-6fec-eeba6879c005"], "ha8749e39g150dg4cc0g98f9g2c951d3ddd91": ["Oh pardon, I didn't want to inconvenience you with my age-old curse.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "053af73c-a7ab-d878-3fae-0f16a93a4f52"], "h3b000295gb3d3g4959gb12bg81b9b80aff35": ["Have a good night.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "93de2fa0-5b96-34d4-4bff-03d94cbb41fa"], "h9a7b36f9gded7g44d9g89bcgcc1a2d717095": ["I'll be your mirror. What do want to know?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "cdb789d8-5fff-9ad5-f7b3-88d08595e102"], "h5679aa69gbbceg4852g8e30gc8b3d13c0346": ["I want to know what the world sees when it looks at me. What you see.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "eda867ec-4ca8-de7e-37c1-04cc37694efb"], "he3ffb667g2143g4ad3g8436gc9f8230d189b": ["Count yourself lucky. I have to see this mug every day.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "d6c82e32-2202-632a-9523-d3cec42f265a"], "hc56753c6g8794g4866gb42cg6bf58921293f": ["Funny. And what do you see, exactly?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "9ecbdb58-a463-6e10-abc1-85aece2a9820"], "h43f4c3fcg78f0g421bga412gb54c39ba9752": ["For you maybe, but I like what I see.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "ef306046-0493-43d2-549e-f368c2792836"], "hb22ea090gb805g4759g9a33g6c410eae34d4": ["It's for the best, you're not exactly ageing gracefully.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "90a1e2ad-28bf-cf9e-445a-94557835906b"], "h07b732ebgc60fg4f2bgafcaga085fc57b2ec": ["Ageing? What do you mean 'ageing'?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "c175dd95-7205-258c-ac63-4a5145d6357e"], "h9b285840g49a8g4d38ga0bfge92166fb2d5c": ["I'm a vampire - forever young.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "4903d75d-16af-7231-0fb4-d38e9bc10742"], "hf0ae9813gc471g495bgb70dg8549ec221168": ["Sure, but was your mole always so... prominent?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "625c2e48-93ff-063e-c5cf-e83d4be2a61a"], "h195700a8g6e50g468dgaa38gabe05b965b0c": ["So is the tadpole causing all that sagging skin, or...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "2272d7b8-2be6-d854-3bdd-b17478dc0850"], "h7590ec83g74d1g4cd4ga2b6gb5d7061cc4ea": ["What are you talking about? My skin isn't... is it?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "92a18a95-a950-f519-aa07-40be533ae749"], "h7eeb6dd0g102dg459fg9a0cg27631bd8e7f6": ["I'm kidding, you look great.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "db891b3a-29ed-697c-ea2d-f5aeee617e2b"], "h7f8a5880g40f5g464ega056gc0182b8a46eb": ["Really? Anything in particular?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "a0d96bd1-62c8-3432-f38c-4a2ff9a9e76b"], "h0155fe37ge362g474ag936ag26302a2897b3": ["You have nothing to worry about - it's a very good face.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "e304f049-faa8-ab8e-f5f2-fd96752a72d8"], "h1f96890ag33d5g488bgaeddg47ec05418505": ["Is it? What do you see when you look at me?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "488811e3-c246-7200-b430-6eee9de45940"], "h96b04c77g9fcdg4bbbg9a95g98a3a7f02cd6": ["Vanity is a weakness.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "f2124b4a-ebe1-f614-436d-e7d9453e3c22"], "hd0369afagd052g4dd1ga311gd6ec2b062264": ["It's an indulgence, I'll grant you, but a weakness? A well-presented face can open a lot of doors.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "76922b41-8753-fd97-0cac-81534429afdc"], "h56139396g43fcg4419ga132g5dd1c13aa1b5": ["Not that I've seen this face. Not since it grew fangs and its eyes turned red.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "cf07adff-0777-dd1f-5273-43dcef10b522"], "haae72f49gc264g4e61ga7a1ga39113b4a786": ["It's a small price to pay for a vampire's power.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "afe09da0-74c1-b26b-97fc-4b22ec5995fe"], "h2c4d3eb0gde77g46e9gbab9gb66710a9d369": ["To you, maybe. To me it's just another thing Cazador took.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "4352e559-e8ed-ed9b-3f1b-46b0eeb44cc0"], "h90f1a7fbgdb26g4a0bgbf4cg3694073523c0": ["Just looking. What are you doing?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "084a0bba-60b5-95d2-c5c9-e5128164fa8e"], "h6f1537f2g6cd9g41b6gab43g49646ed41cd0": ["I'm looking too, but not seeing very much.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "a8e5f924-e6de-3873-4e90-fd1bd97d464b"], "hbd46ec85g1156g4045g94fdgdab0805cbdee": ["Another quirk of my affliction.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "37026b1d-2a0e-fcc6-3600-eed663c46b6b"], "had229dc5g0fecg4abag99ceg79098a677276": ["No, I was just leaving.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "b3a4cb3c-ff96-5a76-1503-4bab9c9ae197"], "h0b4931fdg991bg41f3gb309g873c40150610": ["Suit yourself.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Astarion_CRD_Mirror.html", "5d5b8bc8-d5db-91cb-415c-81a8c716117d"]}